{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_REG_150.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1a,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Ayesha! H-Hellooo!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Tanya, you're as energetic as ever!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, it's been a while since I've seen other people. Plus, I saw you with your friend."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I couldn't stop my excitement when I started thinking about which city she might be from."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Please, tell me about your city.<CR>What's popular there right now?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I wonder... Riesengang is pretty rural, so there's nothing all that special to tell you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "The simple fact that there are lots of people there makes it interesting to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x185,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that pickaxe...!<CR>Did you come here to dig, too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hm? This place doesn't seem to have any good places to dig..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x187,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Oh, so you're not here to mine salt?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Mine...salt? What is this mysterious thing that you're talking about?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Well, the ground around here is all made of salt."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Really!? Even right where I'm standing!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Yes. And it's my family's job to dig it up."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x126,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Whoa, I never woulda known...<CR>Digging up salt..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Tanya's so young, but she works hard every day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x128,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Ohhh, that's impressive.<CR>She's just like me then."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I think I was around your age when I first started at my job."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Back then, I'd get swung around by my pickaxe. It was tough..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Yup, yup, remembering the good old days, when I was so young, is so nostalgic."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I see. Then we are alike!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Yup. So the salt that we use every day is mined here...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Salt is a must-have when it comes to drinks and side dishes. Just like pickles!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I'm very grateful for you and your salt... Can I try digging up a little?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Of course! I'll teach you all the little secrets to it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x46,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Alrighty, I'm pumped now!<CR>Let's dig some up as a souvenir!"
        }
    ]
}